    "Sample: All completed 2024 survey responses linked to registry data.",
    "E.1.6 Workloads and Task Creation Figure E.9 shows that workers who report greater time savings are also more likely to report new job tasks from chatbots Figure E.10 shows the composition of new job tasks from AI chatbots by employer initiatives.",
